entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have helped reduce the number of droids defending the corellian droid factory
entries.journal_entry_description: Destroy ten Super Battle Droids. Reducing the number of Super Battle Droids should help Corsec in striking deeper into the droid factory.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: In order to weaken the droids defences in the droid factory you need to destroy 10 Super Battle Droids.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Report your success to Sargeant Mener
